<title type="html"><![CDATA[7/18(Sat.)Gaming/Women on aging /How Barack proposed to Michelle Obama (Host: Nora)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=411&amp;p=428#p428"><![CDATA[
7/18(Sat.)Gaming/Women on aging /How Barack proposed to Michelle Obama (Host: Nora)<br /><br />Session 1. Gaming <br />In this session, you will have chances to draw or play charade. Come to join the warm up session <img class="smilies" src="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/images/smilies/icon_e_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /><br /><br /><br />Session 2. Women on aging <br />每条皱纹里，都是乘风破浪的勋章和勇气_璐璐的英语小酒馆在线听<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.ximalaya.com/waiyu/4553628/307551983">https://www.ximalaya.com/waiyu/4553628/307551983</a><!-- m --><br /><br />All these information around us,all these messages we get, from the internet,from social media,even from people around us,tells us the aging process is our biggest enemy,especially for women.<br /><br />And this episode is a collection of thoughts on aging from some of the truly iconic women in the English speaking world.<br /><br />Q1.&quot; The way I see it, every year can be a brand new journey.- Oprah Winfrey&quot;<br />What's your comments on this sentence? <br /><br />Q2. &quot;There is a saying that with age, you look outside what you are inside.&quot; <br />What's your opinion on this? <br /><br />Q3. How do you adjust your mentality when it comes to aging? <br /><br /><br />Session 3. How Barack proposed to Michelle Obama <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/PRhZCqAUwsc">https://youtu.be/PRhZCqAUwsc</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Q1. What's your comments on this video? <br />Q2. How did you proposed to your partner? <br />Q3. Do you bring problems from work to home? <br /><br />---------------------<br />Agenda <br />19:00-19:30 Free Talk<br />19:30-19:40 Session 1<br />19:40-20:00 Session 2 Discussion <br />20:00-20:30 Presentation <br />20:30-20:40 Intermission &amp; Group photo <br />20:40-21:00 Session 3 Discussion <br />21:00-21:30 Presentation <br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br />a minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Mon Jul 13, 2020 2:06 am</p><hr />
